PM KISSAN SCHEMA FOR FARMERS

1. Pradhan Mantri Kisan Samman Nidhi (PM-KISAN)

Launched: 2019
Benefit: â‚¹6,000 per year (â‚¹2,000 in 3 installments)
Mode: Direct Benefit Transfer (DBT) to bank account
Eligibility: All eligible landholding farmer families
Exclusions: Income tax payers, institutional landholders, some professionals
How to Apply: Online through PM-KISAN portal or CSC center

2. Pradhan Mantri Fasal Bima Yojana (PMFBY)

Purpose: Crop insurance against natural disasters
Premium Paid by Farmer:

2% for Kharif crops

1.5% for Rabi crops

5% for commercial/horticulture crops
Coverage: Flood, drought, cyclone, pest attack
Claim Process: Through banks/insurance companies

3. Pradhan Mantri Kisan Maandhan Yojana

Type: Pension scheme
Pension: â‚¹3,000 per month after age 60
Entry Age: 18â€“40 years
Contribution: â‚¹55â€“â‚¹200 per month (based on age)
Government Contribution: Equal amount contributed by Govt

4. Kisan Credit Card (KCC)

Purpose: Short-term crop loan
Interest Rate: 7% (can reduce to 4% with subsidy)
Loan Limit: Based on land & crop pattern
Also Covers: Dairy & fisheries

5. Pradhan Mantri Krishi Sinchai Yojana (PMKSY)

Tagline: Har Khet Ko Pani
Benefit: Irrigation facilities expansion
Includes: Drip irrigation, sprinkler systems
Subsidy: Varies by state

6. Soil Health Card Scheme

Benefit: Free soil testing every 2 years
Report Includes: Nutrient status & fertilizer recommendation
Goal: Reduce cost & increase productivity

7. Paramparagat Krishi Vikas Yojana (PKVY)

Purpose: Promote organic farming
Financial Assistance: â‚¹50,000 per hectare (3 years)
Includes: Training, certification, marketing support

8. National Agriculture Market (e-NAM)

Type: Online trading platform
Benefit: Farmers can sell produce nationwide
Advantage: Better price transparency

9. Rashtriya Krishi Vikas Yojana (RKVY)

Purpose: State agriculture development
Support: Infrastructure, innovation, mechanization

10. Agriculture Infrastructure Fund

Loan Limit: Up to â‚¹2 crore
Interest Subsidy: 3%
For: Warehouses, cold storage, processing units

11. National Food Security Mission (NFSM)

Focus Crops: Rice, wheat, pulses
Support: Seeds, equipment subsidy
Goal: Increase food production

12. Pradhan Mantri Matsya Sampada Yojana (PMMSY)

Sector: Fisheries
Support: Pond construction, cold chain
Subsidy: 40â€“60% (based on category)

13. National Livestock Mission

Support For: Dairy, poultry, goat farming
Benefit: Shed construction & breed improvement

14. Sub-Mission on Agroforestry

Benefit: Financial assistance for tree plantation
Goal: Extra income + environmental benefit

15. Formation and Promotion of 10,000 FPOs

Purpose: Create Farmer Producer Organizations
Benefit: Collective selling, better price
Support: Financial & managerial training

16. Micro Irrigation Fund

Support: Drip & sprinkler irrigation
Goal: Save water, increase yield

17. Mahila Kisan Sashaktikaran Pariyojana

Target: Women farmers
Benefit: Skill training, financial support

18. PM Kisan Tractor Yojana

Benefit: 20â€“50% subsidy on tractor purchase
Note: Availability varies by state

